short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: AI powered naming suggestions for your GitHub repositories

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Let AI suggest namings for your GitHub repositories. Open any public repo on GitHub, and use the extension as a client to prompt OpenAI for naming suggestions using the GitHub repository's description and your OpenAI API key.
